> About
solus-installer is an installer for the Solus operating system. It is the successor to the "os-installer" and "live-installer" from Ikey Doherty.
Website: https://solus-project.com/

> Compiling
gcc `pkg-config --cflags gtk+-3.0` -o solus-installer solus-installer.c `pkg-config --libs gtk+-3.0` -Wall --std=c11

> Running
./solus-installer

> Roadmap
* Complete the user creation tab.
* Complete the partitioning tab.
* Add relevant info to the change-log.
* Fill out the timezone list entries.

